snippet.title: [GOTY 2015 #3] Best VGM 1863 - Super Mario Maker - NSMBU Overworld (Edit Mode)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1817 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OIsI5kUyLcI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Super Mario Maker (2015)
NSMBU Overworld (Edit Mode)
Koji Kondo, Naoto Kubo & Asuka Hayazaki
